name: Burt
description: Burt is a 100% fair launched KRC20 meme coin on the Kaspa blockchain. No pre minting, no team token allocation. Burt was just an average Martian chilling on his moon crater, sipping cosmic cocktails and binge-watching Earth's satellite TV. But one fateful night, while scrolling through Earth's memes, Burt stumbled upon something revolutionary: crypto. The idea of decentralized moon bucks got Burt so excited, he packed his space fanny pack, hopped on his trusty space scooter, and charted a course straight for Earth to cash in on the $KAS craze.
